esnik ndaj skuadr\u00ebs] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150207064404/http://www.panorama-sport.com/kategoria-e-pare/xhixha-besnik-ndaj-skuadres/ |date=February 7, 2015 }}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.fshf.org/garat/components/lojtar.php?player_id=215199 FSHF Profile]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Xhixha, Andi}}\n[[Category:1991 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Footballers from Durr\u00ebs]]\n[[Category:Association football goalkeepers]]\n[[Category:Albanian footballers]]\n[[Category:KS Burreli players]]\n[[Category:KF Apolonia Fier players]]\n[[Category:KF Adriatiku Mamurrasi players]]\n[[Category:KF Teuta Durr\u00ebs players]]\n[[Category:FK Tomori Berat players]]\n[[Category:Albanian Superliga players]]\n[[Category:Albanian First Division players]]\n\n{{Albania-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Andi Xhixha\n| fullname = Andi Qani Xhixha\n| image =\n| image_size = \n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|1991|4|15|df=y}}\n| birth_place = [[Durr\u00ebs]], [[Albania]]\n| height =\n| currentclub  = \n| clubnumber = \n| position = [[Goalkeeper (association football)|Goalkeeper]]\n| youthyears1 = 2004\u20132008\n| youthclubs1 = [[KS Burreli|Burreli]]\n| youthyears2 = 2008\u20132010\n| youthclubs2 = [[KF Teuta|Teuta]]\n| years1 = 2010\u20132011\n| clubs1 = [[KS Burreli|Burreli]]\n| caps1 = 20\n| goals1 = 0\n| years2 = 2011\u20132012\n| clubs2 = [[KF Apolonia Fier|Apolonia]]\n| caps2 = 9\n| goals2 = 0\n| years3 = 2012\u20132013\n| clubs3 = [[KS Burreli|Burreli]]\n| caps3 = 29\n| goals3 = 0\n| years4 = 2013\n| clubs4 = [[KF Adriatiku Mamurrasi|Mamurrasi]]\n| caps4 = 14\n| goals4 = 0\n| years5 = 2014\u20132015\n| clubs5 = [[KS Burreli|Burreli]]\n| caps5 = 33\n| goals5 = 0\n| years6 = 2015\n| clubs6 = [[KF Teuta|Teuta]]\n| caps6 = 0\n| goals6 = 0\n| years7 = 2015      | clubs7 = \u2192 [[KF Tomori|Tomori]] (loan)   | caps7 =    | goals7 = \n| years8 = 2016\u20132017 | clubs8 = [[KS Burreli|Burreli]]          | caps8 = 39 | goals8 = 0\n| nationalyears1 = |  nationalteam1 =\n| nationalcaps1 =  | nationalgoals1 = \n| club-update = \n| nationalteam-update = \n}}\n'''Andi Qani Xhixha''' (born 15 April 1991) is an [[Albania]]n footballer who most recently played as a [[Goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] for [[KS Burreli|Burreli]] in the [[Albanian First Division]].<ref>[https://int.soccerway.com/players/andi-xhixha/207888/ Soccerway profile]</ref><ref>[http://www.sportishqiptar.com.al/newsite/2013/01/16/portieri-xhixha-burreli-do-te-jete-nje-kocke-e-forte/ Portieri Xhixha: Burreli do t\u00eb jet\u00eb nj\u00eb \u201ckock\u00eb\u201d e fort\u00eb]</ref><ref>[http://www.panorama-sport.com/kategoria-e-pare/xhixha-besnik-ndaj-skuadres/ Xhixha, besnik ndaj skuadr\u00ebs] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150207064404/http://www.panorama-sport.com/kategoria-e-pare/xhixha-besnik-ndaj-skuadres/ |date=February 7, 2015 }}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.fshf.org/garat/components/lojtar.php?player_id=215199 FSHF Profile]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Xhixha, Andi}}\n[[Category:1991 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Footballers from Durr\u00ebs]]\n[[Category:Association football goalkeepers]]\n[[Category:Albanian footballers]]\n[[Category:KS Burreli players]]\n[[Category:KF Apolonia Fier players]]\n[[Category:KF Adriatiku Mamurrasi players]]\n[[Category:KF Teuta Durr\u00ebs players]]\n[[Category:FK Tomori Berat players]]\n[[Category:Albanian Superliga players]]\n[[Category:Albanian First Division players]]\n\n{{Albania-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Red Director", "label": "safe", "comment": "Adding localshort description: \"Albanian footballer\", overriding Wikidata description \"Albanian association football player\" (Shortdesc helper)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Andi_Xhixha"}
